---
title: Handmade Cheesy Curried Aloo Matar Parcels with Mango Chutney, Cucumber and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Stuffed with curried potatoes, peas, onions and cheese, these easy Handmade Cheesy Curried Aloo Matar Parcels are made by simply scrunching up the pastry around the filling before baking.
